rt%20of%20the%20Ewing%20Marion%20Kauffman%20Foundation%20has%20been%20essential%20to%20the%20success%20of%20our%20Disability%20Cohorts.%20Because%20of%20their%20partnership%20we%20%5Bare%2Fhave%20been%5D%20able%20to%20provide%20four%20Accelerator%20Cohort%20Pitch%20events%20in%202022%2C%20connecting%20countless%20Founders%20with%20Disabilities%20to%20essential%20funding%20opportunities%20and%20exciting%20new%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20id%3D%22w-node-d615e436-da36-787c-f259-7cab6df43f4c-e28d3f58%22%20class%3D%22paragraph-5%22%3E2Gether-International%20is%20excited%20to%20work%20with%20the%20SBA%20%26nbsp%3B%26amp%3B%20National%20Disability%20Institute%20to%20connect%20with%20Disabled%20Founders%20in%20the%20DMV%20area%20and%20beyond.%20Thanks%20to%20their%20support%20we%20launched%20our%20first%20ever%20DMV%20Disabled%20Founders%20Cohort%20in%202022%2C%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20uplifting%20the%20work%20of%20disabled%20entrepreneurs%20and%20small%20business%20owners%20in%20the%20DMV%20area%20for%20many%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20id%3D%22w-node-f5a7a6e5-605b-faac-cde3-c04876259380-e28d3f58%22%20class%3D%22paragraph-5%22%3EOur%20partnership%20with%20the%20Loreen%20Arbus%20Foundation%20empowered%20us%20to%20launch%20the%20first%20ever%20Women's%20Cohort%2C%20connecting%20women%20with%20disabilities%20to%20the%20resources%20they%20need%20to%20take%20their%20high-growth%2C%20high-impact%20startups%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20This%20cohort%20saw%20incredible%20success%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20program's%20alumni%20-%20Keely%20Cat-Wells%20-%20going%20on%20to%20have%20her%20agency%20acquired%20by%20a%20leading%20global%20commerce%20company.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lbbonline.com%2Fnews%2Fwhalar-acquires-disabled-led-talent-management-and-consultancy-company-c-talent%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3ERead%20the%20full%20story%20here.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cimg%20loading%3D%22lazy%22%20id%3D%22w-node-_4a02ebc6-bf7a-4bc2-5a5f-f2a5857290e9-e28d3f5